                     <interp inst="t17771015-6-person142" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I have known the prisoner three quarters of a year; I never heard any thing amiss of her.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17771015-6-person143">
                  HANNAH
                   MOSS
               <interp inst="t17771015-6-person143" type="surname" value="MOSS"></interp>
