                     <interp inst="t17771015-6-person143" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I have known her 14 years; I never knew any thing amiss of her.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17771015-6-person144">
                  THOMAS
                   WARREN
